headline: Jack Henry: Fiscal Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: JKHY) on Tuesday reported fiscal second-quarter profit of $97.8 million. The Monett, Missouri-based company said it had profit of $1.34 per share. The results beat Wall Street expectations.

headline: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc. Reports Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Results
